update_file( src, dst , updatelog=True) 
	Copies files from src to dst if file in dst is different to the file in src.
	Old files are archived in the '\old' folder in their respective directories.
	Changes are logged in update.log if updatelog is set.

total_files( root, levels )
	Counts the total number of files in the given number of levels in root.


treesearch( rootdir, sstring, buffersize, = 65536, search_unicode = False )
	Searches for sstring in all the files in rootdir.

	